<details id="detail-dropdown">
<summary><span class="badge badge-green">semver/goose</span> Dropdown / Select Migration</summary>
<div class="details-content">
<h4>What changed in PF6</h4>
<p>In PF6, <code>DropdownItem</code> children must be wrapped in <code>&lt;DropdownList&gt;</code>. Similarly, <code>SelectOption</code> children must be wrapped in <code>&lt;SelectList&gt;</code>. This is a mandatory structural change affecting every dropdown and select component.</p>

<h4>Before (PF5)</h4>
<pre><code>&lt;Dropdown&gt;
  &lt;DropdownItem&gt;Item 1&lt;/DropdownItem&gt;
  &lt;DropdownItem&gt;Item 2&lt;/DropdownItem&gt;
&lt;/Dropdown&gt;</code></pre>

<h4>After (PF6 вҖ” semver/goose only)</h4>
<pre><code>&lt;Dropdown&gt;
  <span class="code-add">&lt;DropdownList&gt;</span>
    &lt;DropdownItem&gt;Item 1&lt;/DropdownItem&gt;
    &lt;DropdownItem&gt;Item 2&lt;/DropdownItem&gt;
  <span class="code-add">&lt;/DropdownList&gt;</span>
&lt;/Dropdown&gt;</code></pre>

<table>
<tr><th>Criterion</th><th>pf-codemods</th><th>semver/goose</th></tr>
<tr><td>DropdownList wrapper</td><td style="color:var(--red)">вқҢ Not applied</td><td class="winner-cell" style="color:var(--green)">вң… 10+ dropdown files</td></tr>
<tr><td>SelectList wrapper</td><td style="color:var(--red)">вқҢ Not applied</td><td class="winner-cell" style="color:var(--green)">вң… Applied</td></tr>
<tr><td>Test selectors updated</td><td style="color:var(--red)">вқҢ No</td><td class="winner-cell" style="color:var(--green)">вң… 8 test files updated</td></tr>
<tr><td>Files affected</td><td>0</td><td>~20 (dropdown components + tests)</td></tr>
</table>
<p class="footnote">This is a critical gap in the pf-codemods branch. Without DropdownList wrappers, all dropdown menus would fail to render properly in PF6.</p>
