<details id="detail-dnd">
<summary><span class="badge badge-green">semver/goose</span> Drag &amp; Drop Migration</summary>
<div class="details-content">
<h4>What changed in PF6</h4>
<p>DragDrop, Draggable, and Droppable were removed from <code>@patternfly/react-core</code> (even from the deprecated path). The new <code>@patternfly/react-drag-drop</code> package provides <code>DragDropSort</code> and <code>DraggableObject</code>.</p>

<h4>pf-codemods approach</h4>
<pre><code><span class="code-del">// Imports from deprecated path (will be removed in PF6)</span>
import { Draggable, Droppable } from '@patternfly/react-core/deprecated';</code></pre>
<p style="color:var(--red)">вҡ пёҸ This is incorrect вҖ” the deprecated path does not exist in PF6 packages.</p>

<h4>semver/goose approach</h4>
<pre><code><span class="code-add">import { DragDropSort, DraggableObject } from '@patternfly/react-drag-drop';</span>

<span class="code-add">const draggableItems: DraggableObject[] = React.useMemo(() =&gt;</span>
<span class="code-add">  selectedColumns.map(col =&gt; ({ id: col.id, content: col.name })),</span>
<span class="code-add">  [selectedColumns]</span>
<span class="code-add">);</span>

<span class="code-add">const onDrop = React.useCallback((_: unknown, newItems: DraggableObject[]) =&gt; {</span>
<span class="code-add">  // reorder logic</span>
<span class="code-add">}, []);</span></code></pre>
<p style="color:var(--green)">вң… Correct вҖ” uses the new @patternfly/react-drag-drop package with the proper DragDropSort API.</p>

<table>
<tr><th>Criterion</th><th>pf-codemods</th><th>semver/goose</th></tr>
<tr><td>Correct package used</td><td style="color:var(--red)">вқҢ deprecated path</td><td class="winner-cell" style="color:var(--green)">вң… @patternfly/react-drag-drop</td></tr>
<tr><td>API correctly updated</td><td style="color:var(--red)">вқҢ Old Draggable/Droppable</td><td class="winner-cell" style="color:var(--green)">вң… DragDropSort + DraggableObject</td></tr>
<tr><td>Affected files</td><td>columns-modal, overview-panels-modal</td><td>Same files + updated tests</td></tr>
</table>
</div>
</details>

